            "text": "<p>Every bottle of Southern Sunscreen represents countless hours of research, testing, and refinement. We've worked with leading formulators to create an SPF50+ broad-spectrum sunscreen that delivers advanced protection without the traditional drawbacks.</p><p>Our lightweight, non-greasy formula absorbs quickly, leaves no white residue, and works for everyone—from sensitive skin to active lifestyles. It's water-resistant for 4 hours and suitable for both face and body, because sun protection shouldn't be complicated.</p>",
